show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/6tHQuR
show.description: Saanvi’s wedding shatters when her fiancé betrays her with her stepsister. Her stepmother forces her to marry Arun—a scarred, bitter billionaire—or lose her father forever. Thrust into a loveless marriage, Saanvi slowly uncovers Arun’s hidden depths, while secrets and revenge threaten to tear apart the fragile bond forming between them. As loyalty turns to unexpected love, dark motives and buried truths threaten to unravel everything. Watch "Her Husband, Her Stranger" only on KUKU TV!
